data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the heart of Faribault.  Located in a serene neighborhood, this home offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility to schools, parks, shopping, and the unique charm of Faribault.  Enjoy sitting on a new beautiful covered front porch. Main level living room features lots of windows to provide ample natural light, a main floor bedroom, full bathroom, kitchen, dining room, and a den.  Step upstairs to find 3 additional bedrooms and loft area. Basement features stone walls. Do not miss this opportunity to make this house your forever home in Faribault.
